(19, 943, 'Sh.S.S. Chauhan, Chief Chemist, 7880888983', 'Sh.A.K.Tripaqthi, Sc.''B'', Dr. Vijaya Singh,RA , Sh.Ravinder Singh,SRF', '9793407711', 'tripathi_cpcb @rediffmail.com', '', '', '', '152085616616506.pdf', '2018-01-30', 'In view of non submission of verification and implementation status of the recommendations made in adequacy report by NSI, non compliance of CPCB directions, non submission of irrigation plan and based on observations and recommendations of inspecting team, issuance of suitable directions under section 5 of E (P) Act, 1986 may be considered'),
