(32, 1083, 'Punjabi Singh , Manager HR\r\n Mob: 7781007357\r\n', 'Mr. Vaddem Kiran Kumar, R.A-I & Mr. Sudahnshu Charan Mohapatra, R.A-I', '9949363438 /9439107059', 'vaddemkiran@gmail.com  :  scm.101mohapatra@gmail.com', '', '', '', '152352654817154.pdf', '2018-03-09', 'â€¢	The unit was commissioned on 1974 with a licensed capacity of 16 KLPD (Rectified Spirit). The unit has stopped distillation from 2015, whereas bottling plant also stopped from 2016. \r\nâ€¢	Industry was found closed during inspection\r\nâ€¢	Now the unit is under dismantling condition.\r\n'),
