(19, 625, 'Doon Valley Distillers, Kuanwala, Dehradun', '78.10234', '30.23980078', 'Mr. S. N. Mukherjee, Factory Manager', 'Prof. C. B. Majumder, Dr. Rajendra Bhatnagar (IIT Roorkee; Dr. S. S. Rana (SPCB)', '9837790994, ', 'general@doondistillers.com', '152468386312660.JPG', '15246838635789.pdf', '152468386310002.pdf', '152468386320195.pdf', '2018-04-02', '(1) Gas Pressure meter, flow meter, mass flow meter should be installed in UASB reactor (2) MEE design, operation and function should be verified as per design, (3) bio composting plant should be checked for its design, basement detail design, operation and function to meet ZLD (4) complete drying/ incineration is recommended for the MEE concentrate', 'Complied', '', '', '', '', 0, '', 0),
