(21, 595, 'Kishan sahkari sugar mills Sathiyaon Azamgarh', '82.9854093', '25.2610945', 'Mr. N.K. Bajpai', 'Dr. J.P. Chakraborty ( Assistant Professor), Dr. Vijay Shinde ( Assistant Professor), Dr. Lata Kumari ( Scientist, MCIIE), Ms.Zeenat Arif (Ph.D.), Mr.Rahul (Technical Staff)', '7880889019', 'nkbajpai05aug@gmail.com', '152472917015325.pdf', '1524729170850.pdf', '15247291705667.pdf', '152472917018208.docx', '2018-04-07', 'â€¢	Laboratory facility for measuring BOD, COD, TSS etc. should be  created\r\nâ€¢	No efforts are being made for rainwater harvesting and using solar energy\r\nâ€¢	Unit has enough land area to use most of its treated effluent within its own premises', 'Complied', '', '', '', '', 0, '', 0),
(22, 930, 'Kisan Sahkari Chini Mills Ltd.,(Distellery Unit),Ghosi,District-Mau(U.P)', '83.5416604', '26.1314192', 'Mr. N.V. Singh, Mr. Upendra Nath Rai', 'Dr.Pradeep Kumar (Associate Professor), Er. Naresh Kumar shety (Ph.D), Er. Vivek Kumar Pandey (Ph.D), Mr Gopal Srivastava (TS)', '9415844110, 9454168601', 'ghosi.distillary@gmail.com', '15247415038728.pdf', '', '', '15247415031137.doc', '2018-04-07', 'Nothing specific, as the plant is not running.\r\n\r\nOwners should be asked to comply with the CPCB directives and norms and resume the operation as the lively-hood of several families is getting affected. ', 'Temporary Closed', '', '', '', '', 0, '', 0),
(23, 475, 'Kisan Sahkari Chini Mills Ltd.,Ghosi,District-Mau(U.P)', '83.5398032', '26.1403252', 'Shri K. M. Singh, Shri K. K. Singh, Shri Rakesh Kumar', 'Dr. Pradeep kumar, Er.Naresh kumar Sethy, Er. Vivek kumar Pandey, Mr.Gopal Srivastava', '7880889012, 7880889013, 7880889014', 'ghosi.sugar@gmail.com', '152474226628426.pdf', '1524742266891.pdf', '15247422669624.pdf', '1524742266497.docx', '2018-04-07', 'â€¢	Laboratory facility for measuring BOD, COD, TSS etc. should be  created\r\nâ€¢	Several worth considering suggestions have been provided by Vasantdada Sugar Institute, Pune, Maharashtra in their report entitled â€œWater Balance and ETP Adequacy Reportâ€ but the industry has not acted as per suggestions.\r\nâ€¢	Factory premises are not being maintained properly. All over the area was littered with sulfur, ash, etc. Good housekeeping practice is likely to reduce pollution load.\r\nâ€¢	No efforts are being made for rainwater harvesting and using solar energy\r\nâ€¢	Unit has enough land area to use most of its treated effluent within its own premises', 'Non_Complied', '', '', '', '', 0, '', 0),
